divs: Sighting DetailsHaving a smoke on my balcony watching the sky and saw a very bright light that went over my house not making a sound,my jaw dropped and I lost sight after it went over the house.I ran down stairs and out to the front but lost it behind trees.however the same thing was seen in the neighboring city by my 16 yr old cousin.I know what I saw and it wasn't a meteor,shooting star,plane, heli.it was something completely different! I now 100% believe
